OL,5,Cflyover
OL,7,FAmy Sutton meets those feeling the
OL,8,Feffects of the transport disruption on
OL,9,Fthe weekend before Christmas.
OL,11,FNorth East Mayor Kim McGinness has
OL,12,Fsecured an urgent meeting with the
OL,13,FTransport Secretary to discuss the
OL,14,Fdisruption caused by the closure of
OL,15,Fthe A167 Gateshead flyover.
