OL,3,CTransport Secretary to discuss
OL,4,C'escalating emergency' of Gateshead
OL,5,Cflyover
OL,7,FA week has passed since the Gateshead
OL,8,Fflyover was closed due to serious
OL,9,Fstructural concerns (13 December),
OL,10,Fexacerbating congestion in an area
OL,11,Falready impacted by the closure of the
OL,12,FTyne Bridge.
OL,14,FNexus, the travel operator which runs
OL,15,Fthe Tyne and Wear Metro, then took the
OL,16,Fdecision to suspend services between
OL,17,FMonument and Heworth, due to the risk
OL,18,Fof the flyover collapsing.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
