OL,5,Cflyover
OL,7,FBus replacement services are operating
OL,8,Fin their place, with Metros not
OL,9,Fexpected to resume until the New Year.
OL,11,FThe meeting with the cabinet secretary
OL,12,Fis due to take place on Monday 23
OL,13,FDecember.
OL,15,FIn a letter to Heidi Alexander MP, Ms
OL,16,FMcGuinness said: "This now unusable
OL,17,Fflyover is not only impacting local
OL,18,Ftraffic, but is cutting our metro
OL,19,Fsystem in half. We need to ensure
OL,20,Furgent investment to keep our region
OL,21,Fmoving and protect our economy.
OL,26,@xD@ROU
