OL,3,CTransport Secretary to discuss
OL,4,C'escalating emergency' of Gateshead
OL,5,Cflyover
OL,7,F"Local engineers have come up with a
OL,8,Fsolution involving a temporary strut
OL,9,Fto hold the flyover and place and make
OL,10,Fit safe enough to get the metros back
OL,11,Fup and running. I have been told by
OL,12,FGateshead Council this is likely to
OL,13,Ftake 10-14 days.
OL,15,F"I've asked that regional officials
OL,16,Fand those at Gateshead Council and
OL,17,FMetro operator Nexus urgently provide
OL,18,Fyour department with plans, costs and
OL,19,Ftimescales for more permanent
OL,20,Fsolutions."
