OL,3,CTransport Secretary to discuss
OL,4,C'escalating emergency' of Gateshead
OL,5,Cflyover
OL,7,FGateshead Council issued an updated
OL,8,Fstatement yesterday (Friday 20
OL,9,FDecember) which said that they are in
OL,10,Ftalks to see whether part of the
OL,11,Fflyover can be strengthened so that
OL,12,Ftrains can safely pass below it.
OL,14,FIt said: "Discussions are continuing
OL,15,Fwith government ministers, the North
OL,16,FEast Combined Authority, and other key
OL,17,Fpartners to secure the funding needed
OL,18,Fto demolish the A167 Gateshead Highway
OL,19,Fflyover, with plans being discussed in
OL,20,Ftandem around the regeneration of the
OL,21,Farea after that."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
