OL,7,FNexus said they are "closely
OL,8,Fmonitoring" the situation and said
OL,9,Fthat the safety of customers and
OL,10,Femployees is their ultimate top
OL,11,Fpriority.
OL,13,FOn what is one of the busiest weekends
OL,14,Fof the year, the weekend before
OL,15,FChristmas, Gateshead high street was
OL,16,Falmost empty.
OL,18,FA town centre cut off from some of its
OL,19,Ftransport connections, Metros halted
OL,20,Fand traffic diverted.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
